"content_id": "8365",
"reference_id": 0,
"version": "1.0.2",
"title": "8365: wisdom, nature of human",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8365: wisdom, nature of human",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The human quality which enables the planning and successful achievement of a desired goal. It may be expressed as technical skill, practical instruction and astuteness in political affairs. True wisdom includes spiritual discernment and, above all, the reverence and knowledge of God.</p>\n<h2>Wisdom as human skill</h2>\n<h3>For work on the tabernacle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:1\">EXO 36:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:3\">EXO 28:3</a> <em>making the priestly robes</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:2-Exod31:6\">EXO 31:2–31:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:30-Exod35:35\">EXO 35:30–35:35</a> <em>craftsmanship and design in metalwork, stone, wood, embroidery and weaving</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:25-Exod35:26\">EXO 35:25–35:26</a> <em>spinning</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:8\">EXO 36:8</a> <em>making and hanging curtains</em></p>\n<h3>For work on the temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:15\">1CH 22:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:21\">1CH 28:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:13-1Kgs7:14\">1KI 7:13–7:14</a> <em>Huram-Abi, skilled in bronze work</em></p>\n<h3>Other skills</h3>\n<p>Making idols:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:20\">ISA 40:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:9\">JER 10:9</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:17\">JER 9:17</a> <em>professional mourning</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:8-Ezek27:9\">EZK 27:8–27:9</a> <em>seamanship</em></p>\n<h2>Wisdom as instruction in practical living</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:8\">PRO 14:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:11\">ECC 12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:6\">PRO 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:5\">PRO 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:8-Prov10:9\">PRO 10:8–10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:11\">PRO 19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:1\">PRO 20:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:20\">PRO 21:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:11\">PRO 29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:7\">ECC 7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:12\">ECC 10:12</a></p>\n<h2>Wisdom as political astuteness</h2>\n<h3>Wisdom brings political success</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:22\">PRO 21:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:14-Eccl9:15\">ECC 9:14–9:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:13\">ISA 10:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:4-Ezek28:5\">EZK 28:4–28:5</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom in giving political advice</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:8\">GEN 41:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:13\">EST 1:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:11\">ISA 19:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:57\">JER 51:57</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:6\">DAN 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:8\">DAN 5:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:8\">OBA 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:14\">1CH 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:32-1Chr27:33\">1CH 27:32–27:33</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom in government</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:33-Gen41:36\">GEN 41:33–41:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:20\">2SA 14:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:12\">1KI 5:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:48\">DAN 2:48</a></p>\n<h2>Wisdom associated with mystic arts</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:8\">GEN 41:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:11\">EXO 7:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:5\">PSA 58:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:7\">DAN 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:7\">DAN 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:11\">DAN 5:11</a></p>\n<h2>Wisdom as spiritual discernment</h2>\n<h3>Understanding the plan of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:39\">GEN 41:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:12\">JER 9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:18\">REV 13:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:9\">REV 17:9</a></p>\n<h3>Understanding God's ways</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:9\">HOS 14:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:6\">JOB 11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:43\">PSA 107:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:10\">DAN 12:10</a></p>\n<h2>Wisdom expressed in a right relationship with God</h2>\n<h3>Wisdom as reverent submission to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:28\">JOB 28:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:10\">PSA 111:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">PRO 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:7\">PRO 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">PRO 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:13\">ECC 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:9\">MIC 6:9</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom as the knowledge of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:3\">PRO 30:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9\">COL 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom as obedience to God's command</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:6\">DEU 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:34\">PSA 119:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:73\">PSA 119:73</a></p>\n<h2>Wisdom personified</h2>\n<h3>Wisdom calls out an invitation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:1-Prov8:4\">PRO 8:1–8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:1-Prov9:6\">PRO 9:1–9:6</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom teaches what is right</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:5-Prov8:21\">PRO 8:5–8:21</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom existed before creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:22-Prov8:32\">PRO 8:22–8:32</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Human wisdom can be opposed to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18-1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:18–1:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:10\">1CO 4:10</a></p>",
